Game


DEFENSE------------------------------------
HP / 60
AC = 18 CMD
Initiative -2

Miss chance 50%, as Poe are ethereal and spectral in nature.

OFFENSE------------------------------------
BAB, CMB
Scythe +6 to hit, 3d4 slashing. Targets touch.


BEHAVIOR-----------------------------------

Killing gives you a poe's soul, which can be captured in a bottle.
